FileIO Steps:

1. Create a Docker file for the Legacy Application that generates a file and uses socat to make its contents available on port 9090

2. Build Docker file for Legacy Application
	docker build -t legacyappimage .

3. Run Legacy App in a Legacy App Container
	docker run -it --rm --name legacyappcontainer legacyappimage

4. Create a new container which is linked to Legacy App Container. This opens the bash shell of the container
	docker run -it --rm --name linkedcontainer --link legacyappcontainer ubuntu:14.04 /bin/bash

5. Install curl in the the new container
	apt-get install curl

6. Curl to the Legacy App Container at port 9001 to see the contents of the shared file
	curl legacyappcontainer:9001

7. Check the list of linked containers
	docker inspect -f "{{ .HostConfig.Links }}" linkedcontainer
Done
